   <body>
      <p>When the Deal Guidance is based on a Custom Measure and is applicable at the Deal Level
         (Guidance Type), you need to provide custom content for the Deal Guidance pop-up. From the
         cart, you can click <uicontrol>Analyze Deal</uicontrol> button to see the Deal guidance for
         your Custom Measure. In the following screen, you can see that the <wintitle>Analyze
            Deal</wintitle> page provides the Deal Rating for the Margin% measure.</p>
      <fig id="fig_gnc_5m3_rcc">
         <image height="250"
                placement="break"
                width="530"
                href="../attachments/143899590/143899601.png"
                id="image_hnc_5m3_rcc"/>
      </fig>
      <p>You can see that the Column Label for 'From' and 'To' values show the Custom Measure which is Margin percent in this case.</p>
